<p>мқҙнӣ„ createOrReplaceTempView() л©”м„ңл“ңлҘј нҶөн•ҙ Parquet лҚ°мқҙн„°мқҳ лі„м№ӯмқ„ SQL н…Ңмқҙлё”лЎң м¶”к°Җн•©лӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">short_flights_df</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">spark</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">sql</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'SELECT * FROM flgiths WHERE flightduration &lt; 100'</span><span class="p">)</span>
