<ul>
  <li>Filter / Where
    <ul>
      <li>мқёмҲҳм—җ м •мқҳ лҗң мҡ”кө¬ мӮ¬н•ӯмқ„ м¶©мЎұн•ҳлҠ” н–үл§Ң нҸ¬н•Ё</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">voter_df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nb">filter</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">voter_df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">date</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span> <span class="s">'1/1/2019'</span><span class="p">)</span>
