<h4 id="л¬ёмһҗм—ҙ-ліҖнҷҳ">л¬ёмһҗм—ҙ ліҖнҷҳ</h4>

<ul>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">pyspark.sql.functions</code> м—җ нҸ¬н•Ёлҗҳм–ҙ мһҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.</li>
</ul>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">pyspark.sql.functions</span> <span class="k">as</span> <span class="n">F</span>

<span class="n">voter_df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">withColumn</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'upper'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">F</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">upper</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'name'</span><span class="p">))</span>
