<p>withColumn() н•ЁмҲҳлҘј мӮ¬мҡ©н•ҳм—¬ л¬ёмһҗм—ҙ ліҖнҷҳмқ„ н•©лӢҲлӢӨ. upper н•ЁмҲҳлҘј нҶөн•ҙ Nameмқҳ лҢҖл¬ёмһҗлЎң ліҖнҷҳ</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">voter_df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">withColumn</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'splits'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">F</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">split</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'name'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">' '</span><span class="p">))</span>
