<p>мІҳлҰ¬ м „мҡ© мӨ‘к°„ м—ҙмқ„ л§Ңл“Ө мҲҳ мһҲлҠ”лҚ°, мқҙлҠ” м—¬лҹ¬ лӢЁкі„к°Җ н•„мҡ”н•ң ліөмһЎн•ң ліҖнҷҳмқ„ лӘ…нҷ•нһҲ н•ҳлҠ”лҚ° мң мҡ©н•©лӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">voter_df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">withColumn</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'year'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">voter_df</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'_c4'</span><span class="p">].</span><span class="n">cast</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">IntegerType</span><span class="p">()))</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>л¬ёмһҗм—ҙ м—ҙмқ„ м •мҲҳлЎң ліҖнҷҳн•ҳлҠ” л°©мӢқмқҳ ліҖнҷҳлҸ„ мң мҡ©н•©лӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<p><br /></p>

<h4 id="arraytype-column-functions">ArrayType() column functions</h4>

<ul>
  <li>SparkлЎң лҚ°мқҙн„° м •лҰ¬лҘј мҲҳн–үн•ҳлҠ” лҸҷм•Ҳ ArrayType() м—ҙкіј мғҒнҳё мһ‘мҡ©н•ҙм•ј н•  мҲҳ мһҲлҠ”лҚ°, мқҙлҠ” мқјл°ҳм Ғмқё нҢҢмқҙмҚ¬мқҳ ListмҷҖ мң мӮ¬н•©лӢҲлӢӨ.</li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.size(&lt;column&gt;)</code> лҠ” м§Җм •лҗң ArrayType() мқёмҲҳм—җ мһҲлҠ” н•ӯлӘ© мҲҳлҘј л°ҳнҷҳн•©лӢҲлӢӨ.</li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.getItem(&lt;index&gt;)</code> лҠ” мқёлҚұмҠӨ мқёмҲҳлҘј м·Ён•ҳкі  лӘ©лЎқ м—ҙмқҳ н•ҙлӢ№ мқёлҚұмҠӨм—җ мһҲлҠ” н•ӯлӘ©мқ„ л°ҳнҷҳн•©лӢҲлӢӨ.</li>
  <li>мқҙ мҷём—җлҸ„ лӢӨм–‘н•ң н•ЁмҲҳк°Җ мһҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.</li>
</ul>

<p><br /></p>

<h4 id="conditional-clauses">Conditional clauses</h4>

<ul>
  <li>Sparkм—җм„ң кё°мЎҙмқҳ if / then / else л¬ёмқ„ мҲҳн–ү н•  мҲҳ мһҲм§Җл§Ң, DataFrameмқҳ к°Ғ н–үмқҙ лҸ…лҰҪм ҒмңјлЎң нҸүк°ҖлҗҳлҜҖлЎң мӢ¬к°Ғн•ң м„ұлҠҘ м Җн•ҳлҘј мҙҲлһҳн•©лӢҲлӢӨ. ( мөңм Ғнҷ” лҗң кё°ліё м ңкіө мЎ°кұҙмқ„ мӮ¬мҡ©н•ҳл©ҙ мқҙ л¬ём ңк°Җ мҷ„нҷ”лҗ©лӢҲлӢӨ. )</li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.when()</code></li>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.otherwise()</code></li>
</ul>

<p><br /></p>

<h4 id="мҳҲмӢң-1">мҳҲмӢң</h4>

<ul>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.when(&lt;if condition&gt;, &lt;then x&gt;)</code></li>
</ul>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">select</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">Name</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">Age</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">when</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">Age</span> <span class="o">&gt;=</span> <span class="mi">18</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">"Adult"</span><span class="p">))</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><br /></p>

<ul>
  <li>м—¬лҹ¬к°ңмқҳ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">when()</code></li>
</ul>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">select</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">Name</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">Age</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">when</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">Age</span> <span class="o">&gt;=</span> <span class="mi">18</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">"Adult"</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="n">when</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">Age</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span> <span class="mi">18</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">"Minor"</span><span class="p">))</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><br /></p>

<ul>
  <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.otherwise()</code></li>
</ul>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">select</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">Name</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">Age</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">when</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">Age</span> <span class="o">&gt;=</span> <span class="mi">18</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">"Adult"</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="n">otherwise</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">"Minor"</span><span class="p">))</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>otherwiseл¬ёмқҖ elseл¬ёкіј мң мӮ¬н•©лӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<p><br /></p>

<h4 id="мӮ¬мҡ©мһҗ-м •мқҳ-н•ЁмҲҳ">мӮ¬мҡ©мһҗ м •мқҳ н•ЁмҲҳ</h4>

<ul>
  <li>мӮ¬мҡ©мһҗ м •мқҳ н•ЁмҲҳ or UDFs ( User Defined Functions )
    <ul>
      <li>нҢҢмқҙмҚ¬ л©”мҶҢл“ң</li>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">pyspark.sql.functions.udf</code> лҘј нҶөн•ҙм„ң нҳём¶ңлҗ©лӢҲлӢӨ.</li>
      <li>ліҖмҲҳлЎң м ҖмһҘлҗҳл©°, Spark н•ЁмҲҳлЎң нҳём¶ң н•  мҲҳ мһҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><br /></p>

<h4 id="мҳҲмӢң-2">мҳҲмӢң</h4>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">reverseString</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">mystr</span><span class="p">):</span>
  <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">mystr</span><span class="p">[::</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>лЁјм Җ нҢҢмқҙмҚ¬ н•ЁмҲҳлҘј м •мқҳн•©лӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">udfReverseString</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">udf</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">reverseString</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">StringType</span><span class="p">())</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>н•ЁмҲҳлҘј лһҳн•‘н•ҳкі  лӮҳмӨ‘м—җ мӮ¬мҡ©н•  мҲҳ мһҲлҸ„лЎқ ліҖмҲҳм—җ м ҖмһҘн•©лӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<p>м •мқҳн•ң л©”м„ңл“ңмқҳ мқҙлҰ„кіј, л°ҳнҷҳ н•  Spark лҚ°мқҙн„° мң нҳ•мқҙ мқёмһҗлЎң л“Өм–ҙк°‘лӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">user_df</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">user_df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">withColumn</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'ReverseName'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">udfReverseString</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">user_df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">Name</span><span class="p">))</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>м •мқҳн•ң UDFлҘј мқҙмҡ©н•ҙм„ң, мғҲлЎңмҡҙ м—ҙмқ„ м¶”к°Җн•©лӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<p><br /></p>

<h4 id="лӢӨлҘё-мҳҲмӢң">лӢӨлҘё мҳҲмӢң</h4>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">sortingCap</span><span class="p">():</span>
  <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">random</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">choice</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="s">'G'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'H'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'R'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">'S'</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="n">udfSortingCap</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">udf</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sortingCap</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">StringType</span><span class="p">())</span>
<span class="n">user_df</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">user_df</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">withColumn</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'Class'</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">udfSortingCap</span><span class="p">())</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>лӢӨлҘё мҳҲмӢңлҠ” мқёмҲҳк°Җ н•„мҡ”н•ҳм§Җ м•ҠмқҖ н•ЁмҲҳлҘј мӮ¬мҡ©н•ҳлҠ” кІғмһ…лӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

